headline: Radienz Living Announces CPG Executive Thomas K. Hernquist Joins Board of Directors to Lead Growth Initiatives
summary: MOUNT PROSPECT, Ill., July 10, 2025--Radienz Living announced today that Thomas K. Hernquist has joined its Board of Directors to help drive innovation, growth, and provide segment leadership for the company.
